{
  "id": "5fa9da71dff962001ee79dca",
  "title": "文章会話は半二重通信なのか",
  "created": 1604967027,
  "updated": 1605624730,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5fa9da71dff962001ee79dca",
      "text": "文章会話は半二重通信なのか",
      "userId": "5bc5772df30ff700134daa92",
      "created": 1604967027,
      "updated": 1604967027
    },
    {
      "id": "5fa9da8c4daa9200006fde61",
      "text": "[文章会話]は[半二重通信]なのか",
      "userId": "5bc5772df30ff700134daa92",
      "created": 1604967052,
      "updated": 1604967058
    },
    {
      "id": "5fa9da934daa9200006fde62",
      "text": "\tshokai氏はそう書いている",
      "userId": "5bc5772df30ff700134daa92",
      "created": 1604967059,
      "updated": 1604967070
    },
    {
      "id": "5fa9da724daa9200006fde5f",
      "text": "\t\t> 大抵の[chat]は半二重 [/shokai/半二重通信]",
      "userId": "5bc5772df30ff700134daa92",
      "created": 1604967027,
      "updated": 1604967072
    },
    {
      "id": "5fa9da7b4daa9200006fde60",
      "text": "\tただ[音声会話]での[排他制御]ほど強くない場合がある",
      "userId": "5bc5772df30ff700134daa92",
      "created": 1604967036,
      "updated": 1604967133
    },
    {
      "id": "5fa9db4e4daa9200006fde66",
      "text": "\t\t音声会話の場合は[時間による排他制御]がかかる",
      "userId": "5bc5772df30ff700134daa92",
      "created": 1604967247,
      "updated": 1605624670
    },
    {
      "id": "5fb3e3541280f000004e8831",
      "text": "\t\t 声が重なると２人以上の内容を同時に聞くことになる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1605624655,
      "updated": 1605624656
    },
    {
      "id": "5fa9db874daa9200006fde67",
      "text": "\t\t 基本的に誰もこれをうまく出来ないから自然と避けるようになる？",
      "userId": "5bc5772df30ff700134daa92",
      "created": 1604967303,
      "updated": 1604967319
    },
    {
      "id": "5fa9db1f4daa9200006fde65",
      "text": "\t\tそれに対して文章会話、特にチャットは\"同時に\"読む必要はない",
      "userId": "5bc5772df30ff700134daa92",
      "created": 1604967199,
      "updated": 1604967264
    },
    {
      "id": "5fa9daa34daa9200006fde63",
      "text": "   なので[話題のミルフィーユ化]という現象が起きる",
      "userId": "5bc5772df30ff700134daa92",
      "created": 1604967076,
      "updated": 1604967392
    },
    {
      "id": "5fb3e3961280f000004e8833",
      "text": " \t\t [話題による排他制御]を無視するとこうなる？",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1605624721,
      "updated": 1605624730
    },
    {
      "id": "5fa9dc324daa9200006fde6b",
      "text": "    分かりにくくなるだけで、それぞれの話題だけ読んで返答することが不可能ではない",
      "userId": "5bc5772df30ff700134daa92",
      "created": 1604967475,
      "updated": 1604967508
    },
    {
      "id": "5fa9dbe54daa9200006fde6a",
      "text": "   それを誰もが避けようとするか、ある程度許容するかで半二重通信かどうかが決まる",
      "userId": "5bc5772df30ff700134daa92",
      "created": 1604967397,
      "updated": 1604967437
    },
    {
      "id": "5fa9dbba4daa9200006fde69",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5bc5772df30ff700134daa92",
      "created": 1604967355,
      "updated": 1604967355
    }
  ]
}